# Steps

cd

ln -s dotfiles/alacritty/.alacritty.yml
ln -s dotfiles/alacritty/.alacritty.{linux/macos}.yml

ln -s dotfiles/tmux/.tmux.conf

ln -s dotfiles/shell/.inputrc
ln -s dotfiles/shell/.profile
ln -s dotfiles/shell/.profile .bashrc
ln -s dotfiles/shell/.profile .zshrc

After the first start with `zshrc`, run `zle-get-fsh`.

ln -s dotfiles/vim/.vimrc

Run `v +GetPlugs` to install plugins.

`bin/` contains the list of tools which installation instructions depend on distro.
